                        <paragraph>After
mixing, the suspension can be stored at 20°-25°C (68°-77°F). The
container should be kept tightly closed, and the suspension should be
shaken well before each administration. The suspension may be used for
10 days, after which any unused portion must be discarded.</paragraph>
