         <component>
            <section>
               <id root="791bae65-c28d-49c1-b969-9490660a2212"/>
               <code code="34069-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Cefdinir for oral suspension USP, is an
off-white to creamish powder formulation that, when reconstituted as
directed, contains 125 mg cefdinir/5 mL or 250 mg cefdinir/5 mL. The
reconstituted suspension has an off-white to creamish color and
strawberry flavor. The powder is available as follows:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>125 mg/5 mL:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>60 mL bottles                                       NDC 68180-722-20</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>100 mL bottles                                     NDC 68180-722-10</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>250 mg/5 mL:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>60 mL bottles                                      NDC 68180-723-20</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>100 mL bottles                                    NDC 68180-723-10</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Store dry powder and reconstituted suspension at 20°-25</content>°<content styleCode="bold">C (68°-77</content>°<content styleCode="bold">F); [see USP Controlled Room Temperature].</content>
                  </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20120214"/>
            </section>
         </component>
